<div class="abt-intro">
  <div class="abt-img"></div>
  <div class="abt-txt">
    <span class="section-label">The Studio</span>
    <h2 class="section-h2">Where Urban Expression Meets Premium Craft</h2>
    <p>Lacquer Bru is a <strong>multidisciplinary creative studio</strong> built on over 16 years of professional experience across mural painting, graffiti art, illustration, graphic design, textured finishes, commercial painting, and immersive visual transformation.</p>
    <p>Rooted in aerosol culture and evolved through years of real-world creative execution, our work exists at the intersection of <em>urban expression</em> and <em>premium craftsmanship</em>. We specialise in transforming ordinary environments into engaging visual experiences that carry atmosphere, identity, and impact.</p>
    <p>What separates Lacquer Bru is the ability to merge <strong>raw artistic energy with refined execution</strong> &mdash; creating work that is visually bold while remaining sophisticated, functional, and professionally delivered.</p>
  </div>
</div>

